@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### SSO MODULE - Single Sign-On
### ============================================

### PROVIDERS - List SSO Providers
GET {{baseUrl}}/sso/providers
Authorization: {{token}}

### OAUTH - Google OAuth
GET {{baseUrl}}/sso/google/callback?code=AUTH_CODE&state=STATE

### OAUTH - Microsoft OAuth
GET {{baseUrl}}/sso/microsoft/callback?code=AUTH_CODE&state=STATE

### SAML - SAML Assertion
POST {{baseUrl}}/sso/saml/callback
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

SAMLResponse=ASSERTION_HERE&RelayState=STATE_HERE

### Notes:
### - OAuth endpoints return JWT token on success
### - SAML configuration required for SAML login
